text.section:
This section does not apply to:
a transaction undertaken under a contractual obligation in effect on October 1, 1996;
a transaction made in the ordinary course of business of operating a facility;
a refund under a contract entered into in the ordinary course of business;
a transfer of cash, securities, or other investment property in connection with an ordinary investment transaction;
a grant of a mortgage, deed of trust, or security interest to an unrelated third party;
a transaction involving an easement, right-of-way, road widening, or similar conveyance for the benefit of a public body or a utility;
a transaction made for an expansion or renovation; or
any other sale, transfer, or other disposition exempted by the Department by regulation.
